OL,5, Councils will be told to reduce        
OL,6, spending on consultants and diversity  
OL,7, schemes when Chancellor Jeremy Hunt    
OL,8, delivers his Budget on Wednesday.      
OL,10,FCouncils are facing severe financial   
OL,11,Fpressures and eight have effectively   
OL,12,Fdeclared bankruptcy since 2018.        
OL,14,FThis week Nottingham City Council      
OL,15,Fapproved big cuts to services and      
OL,16,FBirmingham is expected to do the same. 
OL,18,FThe Local Government Association said  
OL,19,Fmost councils spent "pence" on things  
OL,20,Flike diversity schemes.                
